---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Delete Account" description="Request deletion of your VoiceCloser account and all associated data.">
  <div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Account Deletion Request</h1>
    <p class="legal-updated">Your data, your choice.</p>

    <div class="legal-card">
      <p>To request deletion of your VoiceCloser account and all associated data, please email us:</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <strong style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem;">Email:</strong><br/>
        <span style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary);">support@voicecloser.io</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.875rem;">Subject:</strong><br/>
        <span style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary);">Account Deletion Request</span>
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <a href="mailto:support@voicecloser.io?subject=Account%20Deletion%20Request" class="btn btn-gold" style="display: inline-block; text-align: center; width: 100%;">
          Email Deletion Request
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-warning">
      <h3>Security Requirement</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>You must email from your registered email address</li>
        <li>Include your full name in the email</li>
        <li>We will verify your identity before processing</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top: 0.75rem;">Requests from a different email address will require additional verification for your security.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-card">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">What Data Will Be Deleted</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Your account and profile information</li>
        <li>Organization and team data</li>
        <li>Call recordings and transcripts</li>
        <li>Agent configurations</li>
        <li>Billing and subscription information</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-card">
      <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Processing Time</h2>
      <p>We will verify your identity and process deletion requests within 30 days. You will receive a confirmation email once your data has been removed.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-danger">
      <h3>Warning</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">Account deletion is permanent and cannot be undone. All data will be irreversibly removed.</p>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/" style="color: var(--text-muted);">&larr; Back to Home</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
